# AI SocialFi - Decentralized Knowledge DAO

A revolutionary SocialFi platform where AI generates crypto research content and users stake tokens to vote on AI-generated insights, creating a decentralized knowledge curation system.

## ğŸ¯ Vision
Transform traditional crypto research by leveraging AI to democratize market analysis while incentivizing community-driven content curation through blockchain rewards.

## ğŸš€ Key Features

### AI Research Engine
- **Multi-source Aggregation**: Scrapes news from CoinDesk, CryptoSlate, Twitter, Reddit
- **NLP Analysis**: Sentiment analysis, trend detection, market correlation
- **Automated Reports**: Daily/weekly research on BTC, ETH, Sonic, and trending tokens
- **Real-time Alerts**: Breaking news summarization and impact analysis

### Decentralized Governance
- **Stake-to-Vote**: Users stake S tokens to vote on AI content quality
- **Reputation System**: Consistent good voters earn higher rewards
- **Content Curation**: Community filters signal from noise
- **Expert Validation**: Top performers can challenge AI conclusions

### Sonic Blockchain Integration
- **Low-cost Transactions**: Efficient voting and reward distribution
- **Immutable Records**: All AI content and votes stored on-chain
- **Smart Rewards**: Automatic distribution based on voting accuracy
- **Cross-chain Bridge**: Support for major crypto assets

